<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5019891>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 147–154. Genitalia of Strigota ambigua (Erichson) (male, paralectotype of St. gnava Casey (149–154); and female, lectotype of St. oppidana Casey (147–148)). 147–148 — spermatheca (of the same specimen; different views); 149 — median lobe, parameral view; 150 — apex of median lobe, parameral view; 151 — median lobe, lateral view; 152 — apex of median lobe, lateral view; 153–154 — apex of median lobe with retracted internal sac, lateral view. Scale bar 0.1 mm (150, 152), 0.2 mm (147–149, 151, 153–154)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/5019891/files/figure.png" .

